1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,000
MkvDrama.net

2
00:00:11,300 --> 00:00:15,423
P'Fah pun agak pandai bab ni, ya.

3
00:00:15,548 --> 00:00:18,571
Hari ni, aku betul-betul jumpa dia.

4
00:00:19,207 --> 00:00:19,880
Siapa?

5
00:00:20,493 --> 00:00:21,531
Orang dalam surat tu.

6
00:00:24,248 --> 00:00:25,985
Gembira berkenalan.

7
00:00:26,462 --> 00:00:27,896
Yang dalam surat tu.

8
00:00:28,208 --> 00:00:29,768
Gembira dapat sayang awak.

9
00:00:31,595 --> 00:00:33,060
Ayah, Ibu.

10
00:00:33,245 --> 00:00:34,411
Kami sedang bercinta.

11
00:00:34,957 --> 00:00:36,198
Rasa macam mustahil.

12
00:00:36,792 --> 00:00:38,028
Tapi hari ni, aku dapat jawapannya.

13
00:01:03,608 --> 00:01:05,250
Saya datang nak hantar dokumen berhenti.

14
00:01:18,103 --> 00:01:19,810
Jadi macam mana? Semua dah selesai?

15
00:01:22,798 --> 00:01:24,568
Ingatkan awak akan menangis teresak-esak.

16
00:01:26,757 --> 00:01:27,915
Aku dah besar sekarang.

17
00:01:28,863 --> 00:01:29,808
Mungkin sebab

18
00:01:30,063 --> 00:01:31,807
ada benda yang aku suka menanti di depan.

19
00:01:32,128 --> 00:01:33,727
Dan kalau aku hantar markah, diterima sini lagi,

20
00:01:34,091 --> 00:01:35,308
aku boleh jumpa kawan-kawan,

21
00:01:36,177 --> 00:01:36,906
dan juga

22
00:01:37,557 --> 00:01:38,894
tinggal dengan awak.

23
00:01:39,435 --> 00:01:40,882
Itu pun dah cukup buat aku bahagia.

24
00:01:43,031 --> 00:01:44,232
Awak memang dah besar.

25
00:01:44,900 --> 00:01:46,351
Jadi kita balik sekarang?

26
00:01:50,188 --> 00:01:53,320
Oh ya, aku kena beritahu mereka berdua dulu.

27
00:01:56,606 --> 00:01:59,570
Hari ni aku dah hantar surat berhenti.

28
00:02:00,940 --> 00:02:02,760
Aku takkan bagi awak pergi.

29
00:02:03,220 --> 00:02:07,753
Jangan manja. Tak perlu rindu sangat,
sebab aku pun hantar portfolio kat sini.

30
00:02:08,286 --> 00:02:10,313
Kalau macam tu, panggil aku senior awak.

31
00:02:10,480 --> 00:02:13,460
Aku arahkan kau, junior Phoon—10 tekan tubi! Sekarang!

32
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:16,126
Ya, bila semester mula, awak mesti jumpa aku.

33
00:02:18,497 --> 00:02:20,816
Phoon, nak singgah mana-mana?

34
00:02:22,617 --> 00:02:24,565
Boleh singgah asrama dulu? Nak ambil baju aku.

35
00:02:27,017 --> 00:02:30,035
Phoon, awak nak pindah tinggal dengan aku?

36
00:02:34,170 --> 00:02:37,005
Maksud awak, kondo awak?

37
00:02:37,330 --> 00:02:38,188
Ya.

38
00:02:38,807 --> 00:02:42,810
Tolonglah. Tinggal dengan awak sekejap pun aku bahagia.

39
00:02:42,971 --> 00:02:44,834
Kalau boleh tinggal bersama selalu, memang best.

40
00:02:46,109 --> 00:02:46,666
Tolong.

41
00:02:48,620 --> 00:02:50,366
Awak takkan bosan dengan aku, kan?

42
00:02:50,631 --> 00:02:54,802
Mana mungkin. Lepas ni tak perlu ulang-alik bilik kita.

43
00:02:58,798 --> 00:03:00,005
Kalau macam tu P'Fah kena tolong aku pindah.

44
00:03:00,423 --> 00:03:04,684
Aku tolong awak masuk—kenapa tak tolong awak pindah keluar?

45
00:03:17,074 --> 00:03:20,105
Nampak macam kamera lagi banyak dari masa awak masuk dulu.

46
00:03:26,591 --> 00:03:27,318
P'Fah.

47
00:03:28,570 --> 00:03:29,057
Ya?

48
00:03:29,351 --> 00:03:30,240
Pasal Fun...

49
00:03:31,017 --> 00:03:33,589
Aku tak beritahu Pak Cik dan Mak Cik terus,

50
00:03:33,651 --> 00:03:36,362
jadi aku rasa tak tenang sangat.

51
00:03:41,265 --> 00:03:42,370
Jangan fikir banyak.

52
00:03:42,589 --> 00:03:44,934
Aku percaya ibu bapa aku akan faham.

53
00:03:51,429 --> 00:03:54,728
Nanti kita balik dan beritahu Ayah Ibu sama-sama.

54
00:04:06,662 --> 00:04:09,577
Jadi ini hadiah yang awak rasa mak awak hantar?

55
00:04:10,713 --> 00:04:11,860
Dalam tu tulis apa?

56
00:04:12,551 --> 00:04:14,450
"Kepada: Ren."

57
00:04:14,862 --> 00:04:18,318
Biar aku teka—Ren nama lama awak?

58
00:04:20,570 --> 00:04:21,499
Siapa yang hantar?

59
00:04:21,583 --> 00:04:22,631
Mak awak?

60
00:04:23,973 --> 00:04:24,882
Kalaulah betul.

61
00:04:26,728 --> 00:04:29,857
Kalau awak rasa mak awak hantar, awak nak jumpa dia?

62
00:04:30,173 --> 00:04:31,112
Nak.

63
00:04:33,623 --> 00:04:36,293
Kenapa, boleh bertukar bentuk ke apa?

64
00:04:38,413 --> 00:04:40,376
Robot edisi terhad.

65
00:04:40,765 --> 00:04:42,902
Dihasilkan awal 2008 di Jepun.

66
00:04:44,059 --> 00:04:45,722
Wah, macam mana awak tahu?

67
00:04:46,157 --> 00:04:47,139
Dulu aku kumpul benda ni.

68
00:04:48,431 --> 00:04:49,400
Aku rasa itu.

69
00:04:50,300 --> 00:04:51,717
Namanya Ren.

70
00:04:52,991 --> 00:04:55,814
Bunyi macam Jepun. Atau mak awak orang Jepun?

71
00:05:00,592 --> 00:05:01,361
P'Fah.

72
00:05:02,709 --> 00:05:06,085
Awak kata awak akan bawa aku ke mana saja aku nak.

73
00:05:06,828 --> 00:05:08,520
Sekarang aku dah tahu aku nak pergi mana.

74
00:07:00,225 --> 00:07:02,330
P'Fah, boleh kita balik sekarang?

75
00:07:03,573 --> 00:07:06,053
Kenapa? Awak baru sampai.

76
00:07:07,232 --> 00:07:10,023
Aku tak sangka sejuk sampai macam ni.

77
00:07:23,760 --> 00:07:24,666
Macam mana?

78
00:07:25,351 --> 00:07:26,444
Dah rasa panas sikit?

79
00:07:34,994 --> 00:07:35,645
Mari.

80
00:07:36,478 --> 00:07:37,297
Jom.

81
00:07:54,794 --> 00:07:55,543
P'Fah.

82
00:08:27,447 --> 00:08:28,509
Hati-hati, sayang.

83
00:08:29,272 --> 00:08:30,678
Perlahan sikit, sayang.

84
00:08:31,549 --> 00:08:33,274
P'Fah, tengok sini. Cantiknya.

85
00:08:34,970 --> 00:08:35,770
Memang cantik.

86
00:08:36,392 --> 00:08:37,191
Terima kasih.

87
00:08:42,654 --> 00:08:44,570
Awak macam patung goyang tu.

88
00:08:59,930 --> 00:09:03,651
P'Fah, nak bergambar? Aku ambilkan.

89
00:09:04,568 --> 00:09:05,786
Kat sini.

90
00:09:47,266 --> 00:09:48,401
Terima kasih.

91
00:09:50,663 --> 00:09:54,028
Jom makan... ya?

92
00:09:54,565 --> 00:09:55,573
Ya.

93
00:10:51,110 --> 00:10:51,845
Phoon.

94
00:11:14,343 --> 00:11:16,152
Kali ni biar P'Fah ambil gambar awak pula.

95
00:11:23,948 --> 00:11:25,491
Tapi aku rasa

96
00:11:26,617 --> 00:11:28,327
macam masih ada yang kurang.

97
00:11:28,973 --> 00:11:30,367
Apa dia?

98
00:11:31,025 --> 00:11:32,801
Macam contohnya...

99
00:11:36,611 --> 00:11:37,696
Macam ni.

100
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:40,305
Ibu telefon.

101
00:11:44,973 --> 00:11:45,897
Hai, Ibu.

102
00:11:45,915 --> 00:11:48,992
- Macam mana, anak-anak? Seronok melancong?
- Seronok.

103
00:11:50,586 --> 00:11:51,619
Fah pula macam mana?

104
00:11:52,885 --> 00:11:55,014
Kalau Phoon seronok, aku pun seronok.

105
00:11:55,241 --> 00:11:58,499
Baguslah. Ibu dan Ayah takkan ganggu kamu lagi.

106
00:11:58,954 --> 00:12:00,488
Baik, Ibu. Jumpa nanti.

107
00:12:01,103 --> 00:12:01,610
Selamat tinggal.

108
00:12:07,877 --> 00:12:08,543
Phoon.

109
00:12:09,962 --> 00:12:11,075
Tentang mak awak—

110
00:12:12,752 --> 00:12:14,521
Sejujurnya, aku pun tak pasti.

111
00:12:14,994 --> 00:12:17,780
Sama ada barang yang dihantar tu betul-betul dari dia.

112
00:12:18,822 --> 00:12:19,823
Tapi...

113
00:12:21,030 --> 00:12:22,926
Dalam hati, aku harap itu memang dari dia.

114
00:12:26,946 --> 00:12:28,650
Datang ke Jepun, aku dah tahu.

115
00:12:29,377 --> 00:12:30,699
Aku takkan dapat jumpa dia.

116
00:12:33,506 --> 00:12:37,510
Sekurang-kurangnya, dapat bernafas dekat sikit pun cukup.

117
00:12:37,908 --> 00:12:39,874
Betul.

118
00:12:59,549 --> 00:13:00,374
Macam mana?

119
00:13:01,190 --> 00:13:03,100
Awak biasanya suka ambil gambar?

120
00:13:05,272 --> 00:13:07,586
Aku jarang sangat pegang kamera pun.

121
00:13:10,610 --> 00:13:11,562
Awak tak suka?

122
00:13:13,294 --> 00:13:14,035
Aku bergurau je.

123
00:13:15,960 --> 00:13:18,873
- Betul?
- Jom pergi ambil gambar kat sana.

124
00:13:19,875 --> 00:13:22,736
Hei, Phoon. Phoon!

125
00:13:27,539 --> 00:13:28,675
Tolong aku sekejap.

126
00:13:29,726 --> 00:13:30,800
Apa dia?

127
00:13:32,586 --> 00:13:34,241
Tolong aku cari mak Phoon.

128
00:13:34,854 --> 00:13:35,804
Mak kandung dia.

129
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:38,553
Kau ingat aku detektif persendirian ke?

130
00:13:39,727 --> 00:13:42,262
Kau nak tulis laporan makmal semester ni sendiri?

131
00:13:43,406 --> 00:13:45,486
Baiklah, aku detektif. Aku carikan dia untuk kau.

132
00:13:46,480 --> 00:13:48,366
Tapi kau kena tolong aku tulis laporan tu.

133
00:13:48,983 --> 00:13:50,522
Ya, aku tolong.

134
00:13:51,680 --> 00:13:52,422
Setuju.

135
00:13:59,790 --> 00:14:01,433
- Aku letak dulu.
- Hei, tunggu.

136
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:07,520
Ia—

137
00:14:08,705 --> 00:14:09,764
Tak pelik ke?

138
00:14:11,598 --> 00:14:12,597
Tak pelik.

139
00:14:13,502 --> 00:14:14,705
Comel sangat.

140
00:14:18,291 --> 00:14:19,102
Betul?

141
00:14:23,705 --> 00:14:24,585
Betul.

142
00:14:28,105 --> 00:14:29,011
Comel sangat.

143
00:14:40,745 --> 00:14:42,146
Budak baik.

144
00:14:48,934 --> 00:14:52,687
Mula-mula aku ingat nak tunggu lagi.

145
00:14:55,041 --> 00:14:59,065
Tapi sekarang, aku dah tak sabar.

146
00:15:24,905 --> 00:15:26,281
Awak milik aku, ya?

147
00:15:42,548 --> 00:15:47,204
Tapi aku dah lama jadi milik awak, kan?

148
00:15:49,109 --> 00:15:51,037
Aku anggap itu jawapan awak.

149
00:17:02,920 --> 00:17:03,880
Boleh?

150
00:17:05,629 --> 00:17:09,457
Kalau P'Fah, apa pun aku okey.

151
00:17:10,259 --> 00:17:11,816
Aku sayang kau, Phoon.

152
00:17:12,940 --> 00:17:14,486
Aku pun sayang kau.

153
00:17:49,545 --> 00:17:51,582
Awal bangun, P'Fah.

154
00:17:55,410 --> 00:17:57,154
Kau yang bangun lambat.

155
00:17:58,857 --> 00:17:59,764
Betul?

156
00:18:01,814 --> 00:18:03,312
Kau okey?

157
00:18:05,634 --> 00:18:06,992
Okey pasal apa?

158
00:18:08,080 --> 00:18:09,288
Err...

159
00:18:09,791 --> 00:18:11,247
Semalam...

160
00:18:13,251 --> 00:18:14,607
Entahlah.

161
00:18:18,069 --> 00:18:19,349
Maaf.

162
00:18:21,690 --> 00:18:23,269
Lupakan. Aku takkan cakap apa-apa.

163
00:18:23,482 --> 00:18:25,508
Hei, mana boleh tak cakap?

164
00:18:25,797 --> 00:18:27,524
Aku yang buat.

165
00:18:29,502 --> 00:18:30,697
Lain kali...

166
00:18:31,250 --> 00:18:33,038
Aku akan lebih lembut, janji.

167
00:18:34,040 --> 00:18:34,891
Janji.

168
00:18:37,482 --> 00:18:39,108
Kau okey?

169
00:18:40,080 --> 00:18:41,517
Kenapa pula tak okey?

170
00:18:43,937 --> 00:18:47,242
Aku takut kau tak suka.

171
00:18:49,207 --> 00:18:50,259
Oh.

172
00:18:51,751 --> 00:18:53,650
Nak aku buktikan sekali lagi?

173
00:18:54,213 --> 00:18:55,410
Yang aku memang suka?

174
00:19:14,007 --> 00:19:14,933
Tak sedap ke?

175
00:19:18,170 --> 00:19:19,088
Aku tak nak balik.

176
00:19:20,579 --> 00:19:22,591
Tapi tadi kau kata nak balik.

177
00:19:23,007 --> 00:19:28,205
Mula-mula aku tak biasa sejuk,
tapi sekarang dah biasa.

178
00:19:29,783 --> 00:19:33,000
Kalau belum nak balik, kita tinggal seminggu lagi?

179
00:19:34,757 --> 00:19:36,345
Kau kena cepat balik ke kelas.

180
00:19:36,977 --> 00:19:40,349
Dan aku kena balik, siapkan diri untuk exam.

181
00:19:41,346 --> 00:19:42,888
Lain kali kita datang sama-sama.

182
00:19:43,878 --> 00:19:44,608
Betul?

183
00:19:45,847 --> 00:19:46,903
Ke mana saja kita nak pergi?

184
00:19:48,008 --> 00:19:49,066
Mestilah.

185
00:20:02,007 --> 00:20:02,657
Phoon.

186
00:20:03,965 --> 00:20:05,911
Boleh aku post gambar ni di Instagram?

187
00:20:06,320 --> 00:20:09,179
Banyak gambar cantik. Kenapa pilih yang ni?

188
00:20:09,694 --> 00:20:11,127
Sebab kau nampak comel dalam ni.

189
00:20:12,080 --> 00:20:12,743
Okey?

190
00:20:39,020 --> 00:20:40,091
Kau nak?

191
00:20:40,337 --> 00:20:41,671
Aku nak bagi pada kawan-kawan.

192
00:21:30,151 --> 00:21:33,992
- Cenderamata dari Jepun.
- Hei, yang mana satu aku punya?

193
00:21:34,226 --> 00:21:36,259
- Yang ni.
- Yang merah jambu aku punya.

194
00:21:36,567 --> 00:21:38,678
Merah jambu kau punya?
Hei, comelnya.

195
00:21:39,117 --> 00:21:41,400
- Terima kasih.
- Hei, ada kucing juga.

196
00:21:41,650 --> 00:21:42,811
Terima kasih, Maew.

197
00:21:44,017 --> 00:21:44,823
Comel juga.

198
00:21:45,866 --> 00:21:48,922
Jadi macam mana pergi Jepun dengan P'Fah?

199
00:21:49,168 --> 00:21:52,268
Manis sangat, kan?

200
00:21:52,288 --> 00:21:54,985
- Apa merepek kau ni?
- Nanti kau buat aku malu lagi, tengok.

201
00:21:55,054 --> 00:21:57,373
- Nampak? Kau dah merah.
- Aku saja nak tahu.

202
00:21:57,414 --> 00:22:00,428
Seronok, sejujurnya. Walau sekejap saja.

203
00:22:00,853 --> 00:22:03,866
Alah, kau boleh pergi lagi selalu.

204
00:22:04,164 --> 00:22:07,725
Ya, macam seronok. Aku tak pernah ke Jepun—aku pun nak.

205
00:22:07,859 --> 00:22:08,977
Habis tu kenapa kau cakap pada kami?

206
00:22:09,124 --> 00:22:13,192
Telefon saja, P'Jo akan tolong tempah tiket.

207
00:22:14,068 --> 00:22:15,143
Baguslah.

208
00:22:16,851 --> 00:22:19,487
Aku suka bila semua orang cerita pasal pasangan.

209
00:22:19,885 --> 00:22:23,265
Terasa sangat suasana yang mesra.

210
00:22:24,118 --> 00:22:27,085
Kau pula? Tak ada sesiapa?

211
00:22:29,724 --> 00:22:30,565
Tak ada.

212
00:22:30,986 --> 00:22:33,176
Tapi best kalau ada orang jaga kau.

213
00:22:33,631 --> 00:22:36,214
- Aku dah ada yang penting untuk dijaga.
- Hei!

214
00:22:36,487 --> 00:22:37,370
Siapa?

215
00:22:37,733 --> 00:22:39,268
Nak aku beritahu?

216
00:22:39,911 --> 00:22:41,493
Mestilah, Dao. Aku nak tahu.

217
00:22:41,570 --> 00:22:43,432
Tunjuklah. Macam mana rupa? Ada gambar?

218
00:22:55,653 --> 00:22:56,345
Err...

219
00:22:57,014 --> 00:22:58,377
Kenapa kau tunjuk aku kucing?

220
00:22:59,192 --> 00:23:01,965
Inilah yang penting bagi aku.

221
00:23:02,714 --> 00:23:04,620
Oh.

222
00:23:05,327 --> 00:23:07,478
- Comel.
- Comel juga.

223
00:23:08,204 --> 00:23:11,840
Cepat makan, lepas tu ke kampus. Nanti lambat.

224
00:23:11,856 --> 00:23:15,385
Aku pun nak balik belajar.
Dah nak dekat ujian hantar markah.

225
00:23:15,705 --> 00:23:17,588
Jangan lupa aku bila kau dah pergi.

226
00:23:17,714 --> 00:23:21,823
- Jangan tinggal kami. Datang balik juga.
- Apa merepek kau ni?

227
00:23:29,269 --> 00:23:30,127
Fah.

228
00:23:30,269 --> 00:23:33,300
- Boleh semak ni? Betul tak?
- Boleh.

229
00:23:38,081 --> 00:23:39,262
Mm, ya, betul.

230
00:23:39,943 --> 00:23:41,571
Okey, terima kasih.

231
00:23:42,368 --> 00:23:45,654
Hei, gambar kau post di IG tu—teman lelaki betul?

232
00:23:46,100 --> 00:23:47,591
Ya. Kenapa?

233
00:23:47,709 --> 00:23:50,583
- Fakulti apa dia?
- Dia nak masuk Photo.

234
00:23:51,297 --> 00:23:52,552
Oh.

235
00:23:53,254 --> 00:23:54,600
- Aku nak intai dia diam-diam.
- Hah?

236
00:23:55,241 --> 00:23:57,354
Gurau je. Kau kuat cemburu, ya.

237
00:24:03,549 --> 00:24:07,939
Hill, dulu masa Phoon belajar veterinar, ada orang minat dia?

238
00:24:08,465 --> 00:24:09,682
Ya, memang ada.

239
00:24:09,995 --> 00:24:11,189
Ter kata ramai juga.

240
00:24:11,411 --> 00:24:12,914
Senior dan sekelas pun ada.

241
00:24:13,251 --> 00:24:14,176
Seramai tu?

242
00:24:14,598 --> 00:24:16,309
Bila dia masuk Photo, mungkin lagi ramai.

243
00:24:16,514 --> 00:24:17,466
Hati-hati.

244
00:24:19,777 --> 00:24:22,380
Fah, ramai orang tengah minat teman lelaki kau.

245
00:24:22,608 --> 00:24:24,262
Kau tak rasa apa-apa ke?

246
00:24:25,574 --> 00:24:28,531
So kalau mereka suka? Phoon suka aku saja, kan?

247
00:24:33,374 --> 00:24:35,832
Aku rasa Hill dengan Jo makin menyakitkan hati.

248
00:24:36,234 --> 00:24:38,368
Tapi kau memang paling teruk.

249
00:24:41,503 --> 00:24:42,417
Kau baik tidur balik.

250
00:24:55,500 --> 00:24:57,060
Buat apa tu, sayang?

251
00:24:58,106 --> 00:25:00,100
Aku tengah belajar.

252
00:25:02,786 --> 00:25:05,810
Jangan lupa makan. Aku dah hantar makanan.

253
00:25:18,260 --> 00:25:20,953
Comelnya. Baik, aku ingat.

254
00:25:22,272 --> 00:25:25,936
Hari ni aku habis lambat. Maaf ya.

255
00:25:29,620 --> 00:25:34,193
Kenapa minta maaf? Kau fokus belajar. Jangan risau pasal aku.

256
00:25:36,460 --> 00:25:41,650
Baik. Semoga berjaya belajar juga.
Aku balik sekejap lagi.

257
00:26:00,560 --> 00:26:01,757
Dah balik?

258
00:26:02,911 --> 00:26:03,650
Phoon.

259
00:26:04,194 --> 00:26:05,614
Kalau mengantuk, tidur elok-elok atas katil.

260
00:26:05,958 --> 00:26:07,520
Tidur sini nanti sakit kepala.

261
00:26:09,733 --> 00:26:11,234
Aku tak boleh bangun.

262
00:26:33,924 --> 00:26:35,983
P'Fah nak sambung belajar lagi?

263
00:26:36,576 --> 00:26:37,213
Ya.

264
00:26:38,029 --> 00:26:40,158
Kebelakangan ni kau kuat sangat paksa diri.

265
00:26:40,628 --> 00:26:42,619
Markah aku tak berapa bagus semester lepas.

266
00:26:43,173 --> 00:26:44,580
Aku nak tebus balik semester ni.

267
00:26:45,275 --> 00:26:46,281
Kau boleh buat.

268
00:26:47,038 --> 00:26:48,010
Terima kasih.

269
00:26:48,657 --> 00:26:50,970
Boleh aku dapat semangat cara lain?

270
00:27:02,282 --> 00:27:02,802
Lagi.

271
00:27:06,105 --> 00:27:06,826
Lagi.

272
00:27:07,275 --> 00:27:08,139
Cukup.

273
00:27:15,362 --> 00:27:16,225
Kau boleh.

274
00:27:17,145 --> 00:27:17,857
Okey.

275
00:27:18,314 --> 00:27:19,429
Aku tak kacau kau lagi.

276
00:27:19,751 --> 00:27:20,475
Selamat malam.

277
00:27:44,526 --> 00:27:46,860
Budak tak guna—berani kau tak jawab telefon aku?

278
00:27:47,093 --> 00:27:49,693
Jangan ingat aku tak tahu Phrae pergi jumpa kau.

279
00:27:49,846 --> 00:27:52,400
- Apa merepek kau ni?
- Pak Cik.

280
00:27:53,220 --> 00:27:55,746
Tonfah? Kenapa kau...

281
00:27:55,856 --> 00:27:58,528
Phoon dah tidur. Ada hal kau telefon?

282
00:27:58,893 --> 00:28:00,917
- Err...
- Kalau tak ada, aku letak dulu.

283
00:28:01,131 --> 00:28:02,811
Tunggu—jangan letak dulu.

284
00:28:13,102 --> 00:28:13,834
Ada apa, Kong?

285
00:28:14,128 --> 00:28:17,945
Aku dengar ada pelabur di Chiang Mai nak bekerjasama.

286
00:28:18,404 --> 00:28:19,453
Mereka nak bincang butiran dulu.

287
00:28:19,908 --> 00:28:21,093
Pelabur?

288
00:28:21,571 --> 00:28:22,081
Ya.

289
00:28:22,497 --> 00:28:23,364
Yang besar.

290
00:28:24,234 --> 00:28:25,325
Baguslah.

291
00:28:25,540 --> 00:28:26,869
Kalau macam tu aku tempah tiket, kita pergi terus.

292
00:28:27,939 --> 00:28:28,607
Kong.

293
00:28:29,327 --> 00:28:32,059
Macam mana hal Phrae yang aku suruh kau uruskan?

294
00:28:32,640 --> 00:28:33,586
Cukuplah, Rit.

295
00:28:34,309 --> 00:28:35,548
Lepaskan saja Phrae.

296
00:28:35,813 --> 00:28:38,865
Diam. Walaupun kau kawan aku,

297
00:28:39,117 --> 00:28:41,097
aku masih boleh halau kau dari syarikat ni.

298
00:28:41,426 --> 00:28:44,647
Kau yang asyik bela budak tu sampai dia jadi manja.

299
00:28:50,013 --> 00:28:52,149
Awak keluar awal hari ini?

300
00:28:53,048 --> 00:28:54,481
Ada urusan sikit.

301
00:28:54,949 --> 00:28:56,281
Bila dah selesai,

302
00:28:56,591 --> 00:28:58,041
P’Fah cepat balik, sayang.

303
00:29:01,312 --> 00:29:03,053
Semoga hari awak baik hari ini.

304
00:29:05,960 --> 00:29:06,700
Awak pun.

305
00:29:17,197 --> 00:29:19,063
Sila duduk dan tunggu sekejap.

306
00:30:05,960 --> 00:30:08,700
Helo, Pak Cik. Lama tak jumpa.

307
00:30:12,260 --> 00:30:14,549
Tonfah, ya? Hampir tak cam awak.

308
00:30:14,757 --> 00:30:15,727
Macam mana awak boleh ada sini?

309
00:30:16,411 --> 00:30:18,188
Orang yang hubungi Pak Cik pasal pelaburan...

310
00:30:18,831 --> 00:30:19,865
itu saya.

311
00:30:20,282 --> 00:30:21,583
Jangan kata...

312
00:30:21,702 --> 00:30:23,106
yang nak melabur dengan saya

313
00:30:23,303 --> 00:30:24,293
awak, Tonfah?

314
00:30:26,521 --> 00:30:28,333
Tapi ada hal lain saya nak bincang.

315
00:30:29,041 --> 00:30:29,922
Apa dia?

316
00:30:30,357 --> 00:30:31,585
Saya terus terang saja.

317
00:30:32,962 --> 00:30:34,894
Boleh tak berhenti ganggu Phoon?

318
00:30:39,829 --> 00:30:41,137
Budak tu cakap apa pada awak?

319
00:30:42,054 --> 00:30:44,625
Phoon tak pernah cakap buruk pasal Pak Cik.

320
00:30:45,241 --> 00:30:46,986
Phoon dah cukup banyak tahan.

321
00:30:47,755 --> 00:30:49,290
Tolong lepaskan dia.

322
00:30:49,724 --> 00:30:51,885
Saya tak pernah paksa budak tu tinggal dengan saya.

323
00:30:52,361 --> 00:30:53,921
Dia je tak boleh hidup sendiri.

324
00:30:54,108 --> 00:30:55,345
Sebab tu dia perlukan saya.

325
00:30:55,854 --> 00:30:57,423
Tapi sekarang Phoon boleh urus sendiri.

326
00:30:57,800 --> 00:30:59,453
Dia dah tak perlukan Pak Cik.

327
00:31:03,797 --> 00:31:05,125
Jadi maksudnya,

328
00:31:05,645 --> 00:31:07,890
budak tu dah berjaya tipu awak, kan?

329
00:31:10,906 --> 00:31:12,459
Mengecewakan.

330
00:31:12,785 --> 00:31:13,684
Akhirnya,

331
00:31:14,023 --> 00:31:15,611
awak rupanya taklah bijak sangat.

332
00:31:19,514 --> 00:31:22,238
Kalau Typhoon berhutang dengan Pak Cik,

333
00:31:22,998 --> 00:31:24,674
cakap saja jumlahnya.

334
00:31:25,060 --> 00:31:26,700
Duit itu satu hal,

335
00:31:27,500 --> 00:31:28,588
tapi budak tu...

336
00:31:28,951 --> 00:31:30,207
dia hancurkan hidup saya.

337
00:31:30,367 --> 00:31:32,278
Dia buat Phrae failkan cerai dengan saya.

338
00:31:44,554 --> 00:31:45,463
Helo, Jo.

339
00:31:45,736 --> 00:31:46,551
Aku perlukan bantuan kau.

340
00:31:54,939 --> 00:31:56,468
Awak nak guna ni untuk ugut saya?

341
00:31:56,619 --> 00:31:57,980
Anggap ini amaran.

342
00:31:58,826 --> 00:32:01,659
Harap awak tahu apa patut awak buat.

343
00:32:08,191 --> 00:32:10,202
Saya akan buat awak sedar awak silap.

344
00:32:10,921 --> 00:32:12,536
Budak kurang ajar.

345
00:32:19,521 --> 00:32:22,357
Eh, P’Fah, awalnya datang sini?

346
00:32:22,758 --> 00:32:23,642
Jo mana?

347
00:32:24,068 --> 00:32:25,155
P’Jo belum bangun lagi.

348
00:32:27,260 --> 00:32:28,662
Awak nak pergi kelas sekarang?

349
00:32:28,840 --> 00:32:31,868
Ya, saya kena pergi kelas, P’Fah. Saya pergi dulu.

350
00:32:38,714 --> 00:32:39,360
Jo.

351
00:32:41,200 --> 00:32:43,333
- Jo.
- North?

352
00:32:44,028 --> 00:32:47,388
- Aku.
- Kenapa kau panggil diri “aku” dengan aku?

353
00:32:47,967 --> 00:32:48,874
Aku ni.

354
00:32:50,280 --> 00:32:52,340
Eh, macam mana kau boleh sampai sini?

355
00:32:53,860 --> 00:32:54,863
North pergi mana?

356
00:32:55,325 --> 00:32:58,075
North dah pergi kelas. Dia cuma bukakan pintu untuk aku.

357
00:32:58,982 --> 00:33:02,228
Kenapa tak kejut aku elok-elok? Kalau aku tersalah angkat kau ke katil?

358
00:33:02,373 --> 00:33:04,014
Nanti janggal nak pandang muka pun.

359
00:33:04,194 --> 00:33:06,149
Nasib baik aku, bukan Arthit.

360
00:33:06,545 --> 00:33:09,354
Ya, dia mesti lagi teringin jadi isteri aku.

361
00:33:09,625 --> 00:33:10,442
Dah, bangun.

362
00:33:14,397 --> 00:33:15,760
Kenapa dengan kau?

363
00:33:18,983 --> 00:33:20,708
Jadi macam mana? Kau dah cakap dengan dia?

364
00:33:21,256 --> 00:33:22,317
Aku cuma bagi amaran.

365
00:33:24,367 --> 00:33:25,768
Menjadi tak?

366
00:33:26,303 --> 00:33:27,007
Entahlah.

367
00:33:28,188 --> 00:33:29,400
Kau dah cakap dengan dia?

368
00:33:29,900 --> 00:33:31,373
Kalau Phoon tak nak kita campur tangan,

369
00:33:32,567 --> 00:33:33,617
kita memang menyibuk.

370
00:33:33,960 --> 00:33:34,610
Dan...

371
00:33:34,868 --> 00:33:36,429
kalau akhirnya Phoon pilih ayah dia,

372
00:33:37,619 --> 00:33:38,829
dan putus dengan kau, kau nak buat apa?

373
00:33:41,411 --> 00:33:43,625
Eh, aku cakap andaian je.

374
00:33:44,565 --> 00:33:46,167
Apa kau buat tu mungkin jadi.

375
00:33:49,527 --> 00:33:50,468
Oh, ya...

376
00:33:51,371 --> 00:33:52,986
macam mana hal yang kau suruh aku siasat tu?

377
00:33:53,434 --> 00:33:56,109
Tenang. Aku dah hantar orang semak.

378
00:33:57,308 --> 00:33:58,466
Tak ada perkembangan langsung?

379
00:33:59,059 --> 00:34:01,100
Mereka masih kumpul maklumat.

380
00:34:01,776 --> 00:34:02,234
Tapi...

381
00:34:03,232 --> 00:34:04,776
kau kata

382
00:34:05,050 --> 00:34:06,964
mak Phoon mungkin orang Jepun, kan?

383
00:34:07,562 --> 00:34:08,080
Ya.

384
00:34:09,595 --> 00:34:10,629
Mungkin Phoon betul.

385
00:34:28,691 --> 00:34:29,671
Awal dah balik?

386
00:34:30,629 --> 00:34:31,680
Dah balik.

387
00:34:32,306 --> 00:34:33,377
Awak buat apa?

388
00:34:34,386 --> 00:34:36,797
Saya cuba tulis sikit bahasa Jepun.

389
00:34:37,404 --> 00:34:38,711
Bahasa Jepun?

390
00:34:39,509 --> 00:34:41,533
Mana tahu saya dapat cakap dengan mak saya.

391
00:34:41,955 --> 00:34:46,214
Wah, hebatnya. P’Fah ada ganjaran untuk budak baik.

392
00:34:46,490 --> 00:34:47,031
Hm?

393
00:34:47,960 --> 00:34:53,253
Phoon, ingat tak awak suruh saya minta Jo siasat pasal mak awak?

394
00:34:54,937 --> 00:34:57,254
Sekarang nampaknya mak awak memang di Jepun.

395
00:34:57,872 --> 00:35:01,068
Tapi kita belum jumpa lagi. Mereka teruskan cari.

396
00:35:02,122 --> 00:35:03,801
- Betul?
- Betul.

397
00:35:04,770 --> 00:35:05,884
Terima kasih, P’Fah.

398
00:35:32,114 --> 00:35:32,854
Phoon.

399
00:35:34,691 --> 00:35:35,979
Sebenarnya...

400
00:35:36,542 --> 00:35:38,601
hari ini saya jumpa ayah awak.

401
00:35:39,602 --> 00:35:41,097
Ayah awak telefon semalam.

402
00:35:47,687 --> 00:35:49,675
Maaf saya tak beritahu awal-awal, Phoon.

403
00:35:50,518 --> 00:35:51,568
Saya cuma fikir

404
00:35:52,260 --> 00:35:54,173
awak tak begitu nak cakap pasal ayah awak.

405
00:35:54,527 --> 00:35:56,500
Jadi saya tak berani tanya betul-betul.

406
00:35:57,262 --> 00:35:58,838
Saya risau pasal awak, Phoon.

407
00:36:00,588 --> 00:36:01,871
Bukan macam tu.

408
00:36:02,597 --> 00:36:03,906
Saya cuma...

409
00:36:04,611 --> 00:36:07,703
tak tahu macam mana nak mula cerita.

410
00:36:08,808 --> 00:36:10,917
Dah lama saya tak hubungi ayah saya.

411
00:36:12,066 --> 00:36:13,472
Saya rasa...

412
00:36:14,720 --> 00:36:16,160
lebih baik putuskan hubungan macam ni.

413
00:36:17,414 --> 00:36:19,494
Masa awak jauhkan diri daripada saya dulu...

414
00:36:21,127 --> 00:36:22,557
sebab ayah awak ke?

415
00:36:31,374 --> 00:36:32,448
Kalau...

416
00:36:32,714 --> 00:36:34,773
ayah awak suruh awak berhenti jumpa saya lagi,

417
00:36:35,724 --> 00:36:37,053
awak akan ikut?

418
00:36:37,868 --> 00:36:39,149
Ayah saya cakap macam tu?

419
00:36:39,789 --> 00:36:40,731
Tak.

420
00:36:41,217 --> 00:36:42,640
Saya cuma tanya, mana tahu.

421
00:36:43,820 --> 00:36:45,040
Sebenarnya...

422
00:36:45,699 --> 00:36:47,659
dari awal ayah saya tak nak saya dengan awak.

423
00:36:48,247 --> 00:36:50,068
Tapi kalau dia suruh saya berhenti sekarang...

424
00:36:53,771 --> 00:36:54,866
saya takkan buat.

425
00:37:00,868 --> 00:37:02,237
Itu dah lebih daripada cukup

426
00:37:02,266 --> 00:37:03,171
untuk saya, Phoon.

427
00:37:04,085 --> 00:37:05,822
Awak tak perlu risau apa-apa lagi.

428
00:37:06,511 --> 00:37:08,097
Semua akan selesai.

429
00:37:09,500 --> 00:37:10,880
Percayakan saya, sayang.

430
00:37:27,566 --> 00:37:30,493
Akhirnya, Phoon pilih aku.

431
00:37:32,200 --> 00:37:34,066
Pilih apa?

432
00:37:35,753 --> 00:37:38,000
Dia kata dia takkan putus dengan aku.

433
00:37:38,940 --> 00:37:40,900
Apa?

434
00:37:48,909 --> 00:37:52,139
Maaf. Kebelakangan ni saya tak banyak masa untuk awak.

435
00:37:52,429 --> 00:37:53,737
P’Fah fikir berlebihan lagi.

436
00:37:54,296 --> 00:37:55,048
Tak apa.

437
00:37:55,311 --> 00:37:57,360
Saya akan suruh Ter dan North datang.

438
00:37:57,845 --> 00:37:59,115
Awak pun fokus belajar.

439
00:37:59,514 --> 00:38:00,654
Saya baca sambil tunggu awak.

440
00:38:01,087 --> 00:38:01,758
Okey.

441
00:38:02,370 --> 00:38:03,527
Telefon saya kalau ada apa-apa.

442
00:38:17,626 --> 00:38:21,260
Aku di kafe depan kampus. Lepas kelas cepat datang. Sunyi.

443
00:38:22,580 --> 00:38:24,746
Aku pun sunyi. Kau tinggal aku.

444
00:38:25,033 --> 00:38:27,646
Kau masih merajuk?

445
00:38:28,786 --> 00:38:33,246
Pergi belajar elok-elok. Baca buku, budak berhenti sekolah.

446
00:38:33,540 --> 00:38:35,506
Aku masih jauh lagi.

447
00:38:37,413 --> 00:38:39,753
Belajar rajin-rajin, Dao.

448
00:38:40,026 --> 00:38:41,720
Rindu kau, Maew.

449
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:44,966
Aku nak siap dah. Kau belanja green tea frappe.

450
00:38:46,486 --> 00:38:47,706
Baik.

451
00:39:03,875 --> 00:39:05,139
Ya, Mak Cik Phrae.

452
00:39:05,533 --> 00:39:09,526
Dia siap ugut, kata nak bawa Fai tinggal dengan dia.

453
00:39:09,760 --> 00:39:14,873
Maaf sebab bebankan semua ni pada awak.
Tak ada orang lain nak dengar.

454
00:39:15,718 --> 00:39:19,050
Selain dengar, tak banyak aku boleh buat.

455
00:39:19,486 --> 00:39:22,666
Jangan cakap macam tu. Awak dah banyak bantu saya.

456
00:39:23,494 --> 00:39:26,177
Saya cuba cakap dengan pasangan saya.

457
00:39:26,622 --> 00:39:28,000
Mungkin dia boleh bantu apa-apa.

458
00:39:28,086 --> 00:39:34,166
Terima kasih. Terima kasih banyak-banyak.
Awak sudi dengar pun dah bermakna.

459
00:39:35,063 --> 00:39:38,011
Aku nak bantu. Fai adik aku.

460
00:39:50,817 --> 00:39:54,017
Apa kau cakap pada Tonfah sampai dia layan aku macam ni?

461
00:39:54,265 --> 00:39:55,100
Layan kau macam mana?

462
00:39:55,367 --> 00:39:58,514
Macam mana? Kau tak tahu mengenang budi, sial.

463
00:39:58,856 --> 00:40:01,474
Hal Phrae ni semua sebab kau, kan?

464
00:40:01,648 --> 00:40:04,724
Kau dah ambil Thorfun. Masih tak puas?

465
00:40:04,921 --> 00:40:08,091
Apa kau buat ni buat aku hilang isteri dan anak.

466
00:40:08,604 --> 00:40:11,546
Sial kau. Sampai bila kau nak hancurkan hidup aku?

467
00:40:12,183 --> 00:40:14,466
Patutnya dulu aku tak bagi perempuan tu lahirkan kau.

468
00:40:14,873 --> 00:40:16,373
Kalau begitu, kenapa biar aku lahir?

469
00:40:17,620 --> 00:40:19,350
Kalau kau tak pernah sayang atau peduli pun.

470
00:40:19,726 --> 00:40:21,070
Aku ada minta dilahirkan?

471
00:40:24,271 --> 00:40:25,503
Kalau aku boleh pilih...

472
00:40:26,013 --> 00:40:28,059
kau ingat aku akan pilih kau jadi ayah aku?

473
00:40:29,260 --> 00:40:30,619
Aku tak boleh pilih itu.

474
00:40:30,962 --> 00:40:32,668
Kau yang ada pilihan.

475
00:40:33,471 --> 00:40:36,228
Aku ni akibat perbuatan kau.

476
00:40:36,533 --> 00:40:37,937
Tanggunglah sikit.

477
00:40:38,151 --> 00:40:40,477
Aku suruh perempuan tu gugurkan kau.

478
00:40:40,911 --> 00:40:42,434
Aku tak pernah pilih kau.

479
00:40:42,811 --> 00:40:45,037
Aku tak pernah nak kau lahir.

480
00:40:45,826 --> 00:40:46,835
Perempuan tu...

481
00:40:47,071 --> 00:40:48,807
dia bodoh dan degil.

482
00:40:49,297 --> 00:40:50,656
Dia pilih untuk simpan kau.

483
00:40:50,965 --> 00:40:52,737
Dan akhirnya, dia tinggalkan kau juga.

484
00:40:53,023 --> 00:40:55,241
Tak ada siapa pun tahu dia di mana sekarang.

485
00:40:55,755 --> 00:40:58,241
Dan kau ingat Mak Cik Phrae tinggalkan kau sebab aku?

486
00:40:59,097 --> 00:41:00,463
Dia nak besarkan Fai sendiri.

487
00:41:01,294 --> 00:41:03,554
Sebab kau terlalu teruk untuk jadi ayah.

488
00:41:03,903 --> 00:41:06,762
Teruk sangat sampai dia tak nak kau sentuh anak perempuan dia.

489
00:41:07,031 --> 00:41:08,071
Mulut besar.

490
00:41:08,626 --> 00:41:10,106
Kau cari pasal.

491
00:41:10,611 --> 00:41:11,678
Hei, North!

492
00:41:12,669 --> 00:41:15,422
- North, cukup.
- Orang sial ni memang patut!

493
00:41:16,641 --> 00:41:18,025
Cukup!

494
00:41:18,465 --> 00:41:20,020
Budak tak guna, kau tumbuk aku!

495
00:41:20,360 --> 00:41:21,648
Aku akan ingat hal ni.

496
00:41:22,070 --> 00:41:23,345
Jaga kawan kau.

497
00:41:23,628 --> 00:41:28,506
- Padam muka kau! Siapa kau sebenarnya?
- Bertenang, North.

498
00:41:29,453 --> 00:41:31,037
Hah? Ayah kau?

499
00:41:31,361 --> 00:41:33,327
Lelaki tadi tu ayah kau?

500
00:41:33,622 --> 00:41:34,314
Ya.

501
00:41:34,718 --> 00:41:37,220
Aku nampak dia nak pukul kau, jadi aku pukul dulu.

502
00:41:38,303 --> 00:41:41,770
Sial, aku tak pernah tumbuk ayah kawan seumur hidup aku.

503
00:41:42,674 --> 00:41:45,330
Tak apa. Kau cuma cuba tolong aku.

504
00:41:45,924 --> 00:41:48,925
Ayah jenis apa pukul anak macam nak bunuh?

505
00:41:51,231 --> 00:41:53,734
- Sakit tak?
- Memang sakitlah.

506
00:41:53,921 --> 00:41:54,668
Maaf.

507
00:41:56,518 --> 00:41:58,202
Aku nak cakap apa pada P'Jo?

508
00:41:59,845 --> 00:42:01,482
Cakap aku alah pada cili?

509
00:42:02,560 --> 00:42:03,574
Kau rasa dia percaya?

510
00:42:04,051 --> 00:42:05,920
Atau cakap aku minum wain,

511
00:42:06,380 --> 00:42:07,103
lepas tu pening sikit.

512
00:42:08,041 --> 00:42:08,850
Aduh.

513
00:42:10,026 --> 00:42:11,471
P'Jo akan percaya aku ke?

514
00:42:14,308 --> 00:42:14,930
Hei.

515
00:42:17,244 --> 00:42:17,882
North.

516
00:42:18,240 --> 00:42:19,592
Mereka kata kau kena pukul?

517
00:42:19,681 --> 00:42:20,755
Kau okey?

518
00:42:35,226 --> 00:42:35,998
Sakit tak?

519
00:42:39,641 --> 00:42:40,392
Fah.

520
00:42:40,810 --> 00:42:41,684
Mari cakap dengan aku sekejap.

521
00:42:43,192 --> 00:42:43,637
Okey.

522
00:42:44,863 --> 00:42:46,675
Hill, kau teman mereka dulu.

523
00:42:59,451 --> 00:43:01,121
Aku ingat cakap baik-baik boleh masuk pada dia.

524
00:43:01,638 --> 00:43:03,442
Kalau kau tak buat apa-apa, aku urus sendiri.

525
00:43:03,773 --> 00:43:04,405
Bertenang dulu.

526
00:43:04,765 --> 00:43:06,154
Macam mana aku nak bertenang?

527
00:43:06,865 --> 00:43:08,198
Kalau begitu, bertenanglah untuk aku, ya.

528
00:43:11,025 --> 00:43:12,564
Aku kena buat sesuatu pasal ni.

529
00:43:15,034 --> 00:43:16,752
Apa maksud kau akaun dah dibekukan?

530
00:43:17,395 --> 00:43:19,665
Kau gila? Macam mana boleh jadi? Kau dah semak betul-betul?

531
00:43:19,800 --> 00:43:21,034
Serah diri, Rit.

532
00:43:21,560 --> 00:43:24,240
Apa kau cakap? Berani kau cakap dengan aku macam tu?

533
00:43:26,995 --> 00:43:27,848
Tonfah.

534
00:43:29,001 --> 00:43:30,091
Tapi macam mana dia boleh buat begini?

535
00:43:30,191 --> 00:43:32,371
Aku dah bersihkan semua.

536
00:43:35,278 --> 00:43:36,388
Kapten, Sarjan.

537
00:43:36,982 --> 00:43:38,554
Tuan, tangkap saya atas sebab apa?

538
00:43:38,915 --> 00:43:42,508
Tuan, tunggu—lepaskan dulu. Kita duduk bincang.

539
00:43:42,588 --> 00:43:43,737
Tuan tak boleh tangkap saya macam ni saja.

540
00:43:43,830 --> 00:43:50,680
Ia menggemparkan dunia perniagaan.
Seorang ahli perniagaan terkenal dan bekas eksekutif kanan syarikat hartanah terkemuka

541
00:43:50,753 --> 00:43:54,093
ditahan polis di bilik hotelnya ketika bersiap untuk melarikan diri.

542
00:43:54,620 --> 00:43:57,760
Dia kini suspek kes pecah amanah dan pengubahan wang haram.

543
00:43:57,909 --> 00:43:59,960
Itu kerja kau dengan P'Jo?

544
00:44:07,450 --> 00:44:09,622
Mula-mula aku ingat dia takkan ganggu kau lagi.

545
00:44:13,284 --> 00:44:14,659
Tapi lepas tu dia buat macam ni.

546
00:44:18,358 --> 00:44:19,324
Sejujurnya,

547
00:44:19,619 --> 00:44:21,613
aku dah lama risau pasal ayah kau.

548
00:44:22,496 --> 00:44:24,487
Jadi aku minta Jo siasat sikit.

549
00:44:25,182 --> 00:44:27,831
Macam tu kami jumpa bukti pecah amanah dan pengubahan wang haram.

550
00:44:28,724 --> 00:44:29,496
Pada awalnya,

551
00:44:30,234 --> 00:44:32,525
aku cuma nak guna untuk takutkan dia supaya dia tinggalkan kau.

552
00:44:33,385 --> 00:44:35,128
Tapi sebab dia pilih buat begini,

553
00:44:37,440 --> 00:44:39,121
aku kena buat perkara yang betul.

554
00:44:41,623 --> 00:44:42,897
Kau marah aku, Phoon?

555
00:44:45,878 --> 00:44:47,411
Kenapa aku nak marah kau?

556
00:44:49,954 --> 00:44:52,151
Memang itu yang dia patut dapat.

557
00:44:52,530 --> 00:44:54,760
Encik Ritchai mengaku kepada pihak berkuasa

558
00:44:54,840 --> 00:44:57,840
bahawa dia terlibat dalam pemindahan wang secara tidak sah,

559
00:44:58,446 --> 00:45:04,100
termasuk perniagaan bawah urusannya yang mungkin terkait operasi kelabu di negara jiran.

560
00:45:04,220 --> 00:45:08,426
Pihak berkuasa kini menyemak rekod kewangan beberapa tahun.

561
00:45:08,646 --> 00:45:09,780
Dulu,

562
00:45:10,484 --> 00:45:12,808
dia sangat bangga dengan imej dia.

563
00:45:13,179 --> 00:45:16,675
Sekarang muka pun dia kena sorok.

564
00:45:18,136 --> 00:45:19,601
Aku sangat ambil berat pasal dia,

565
00:45:20,714 --> 00:45:22,717
buat semua yang dia nak aku jadi,

566
00:45:24,017 --> 00:45:25,736
harap dia sayang aku balik.

567
00:45:27,717 --> 00:45:28,626
Tapi dia tak pernah pun.

568
00:45:30,909 --> 00:45:31,964
Akhirnya,

569
00:45:32,765 --> 00:45:33,979
aku ditinggalkan seorang diri.

570
00:45:38,388 --> 00:45:39,703
Kenapa kau cakap macam tu?

571
00:45:40,411 --> 00:45:41,494
Kau ada aku.

572
00:45:42,534 --> 00:45:43,826
Kau masih ada aku.

573
00:45:44,468 --> 00:45:46,900
Jangan fikir kau kena bersendirian lagi.

574
00:45:47,591 --> 00:45:49,155
Nanti aku sedih, tau.

575
00:45:51,906 --> 00:45:52,859
Maaf.

576
00:45:54,517 --> 00:45:55,733
Kau akan sentiasa ada aku.

577
00:46:25,902 --> 00:46:26,645
Kau pergi mana?

578
00:46:27,228 --> 00:46:28,554
Aku turun ambil sesuatu dekat bawah.

579
00:46:29,219 --> 00:46:30,388
Jo yang hantar.

580
00:46:32,520 --> 00:46:33,680
Berita baik.

581
00:46:36,682 --> 00:46:37,360
Apa dia?

582
00:46:55,748 --> 00:46:56,565
Mak.

583
00:47:13,035 --> 00:47:13,948
P'Fah.

584
00:47:15,115 --> 00:47:15,645
Ya?

585
00:47:16,149 --> 00:47:17,842
Mak mesti dapatkan aku masa dia langsung tak bersedia.

586
00:47:18,588 --> 00:47:19,733
Kau nak jumpa dia?

587
00:47:20,374 --> 00:47:23,120
Aku rasa kau patut. Dia mesti sangat rindu kau.

588
00:47:23,960 --> 00:47:27,040
Mungkin dia tak nak jumpa aku.

589
00:47:28,020 --> 00:47:29,457
Sebab itu dia tak pernah balas surat aku.

590
00:47:30,232 --> 00:47:31,496
Kenapa awak fikir begitu?

591
00:47:32,179 --> 00:47:34,884
Mungkin aku cuma tak biasa rasa bahagia.

592
00:47:36,397 --> 00:47:39,450
Aku betul-betul minta maaf.

593
00:47:39,731 --> 00:47:41,884
Ibu sayang awak.

